<P>THE
GENTLEMAN
FARMER.</P>
<P>BEING
An Attempt to improve
AGRICULTURE,
By &s;ubjecting it to the Te&s;t
OF
RATIONAL PRINCIPLES.</P>
<Q>Semper ego auditor tantum?</Q>
<BIBL>JUV.</BIBL>
