<P><HI>N. B.</HI> The expence of the hou&s;e for holding
the hu&s;bandry in&s;truments, is not taken into this
account; becau&s;e every farm ought to be provi|ded
with &s;uch a hou&s;e, whatever be the con&s;truc|tion
of the other farm-offices.</P>
